    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Summarizing a conversation with @fperez from last week:\n\nWe should add the notion, and corresponding UI, of cell-level magics.  Currently, the two we have are `%autopx` and `%loadpy`, which don't make a lot of sense in the notebook as regular code (it makes sense to use them, but it doesn't make a lot of sense to _save_ a notebook with `%loadpy` or `%autopx` in it right now).\n\nThe magics system is the next thing in line for major overhaul, and @fperez has a solid idea of what it will look like.\n"
  },
