    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It's a tricky problem.  When I use %loadpy, it's always one of two cases:\n1. IPython demo, where I only ever want to save the `%loadpy` call, never the results.\n2. Personal use, where I just want to get the code from somewhere (never keep `%loadpy`, only results).\n\nIn both cases, `%loadpy` and its output really correspond to _one_ cell, and I never want to save both in a document.\n"
